quran[9{c,v,t}:
40,8,"ae hamaray rab, aur daakhil kar unn ko hamesha rehne wali unnjannaton mein jin ka to ne unn se wada kya hai, aur unn ke walidain aur biwion aur aulaad mein se jo Saleh hon ( unn ko bhi wahan unn ke sath pouncha day ) to bulaa shuba Qadir mutlaq aur hakeem hai"
40,9,"aur bacha day unn ko buraiyon se jis ko to ne qayamat ke din buraiyon se bacha diya uss par to ne bara reham kya, yahi barri kamyabi hai """
40,10,"jin logon ne kufar kya hai, qayamat ke roz unn ko pukaar kar kaha jaye ga"" aaj tumhe jitna shadeed gussa apne oopar aa raha hai, Allah tum par uss se ziyada ghazab naak uss waqt hota tha jab tumhe imaan ki taraf bulaya jata tha aur tum kufar karte thay """
40,11,"woh kahin ge"" ae hamaray rab, to ne waqai hamein do dafaa mout aur do dafaa zindagi day di, ab hum apneKasoroo-n ka aitraaf karte hain, kya ab yahan se niklny ki bhi koi Sabeel hai? """
40,12,"( jawab miley ga )"" yeh haalat jis mein tum mubtala ho, iss wajah se hai ke jab akailey Allah ki taraf bulaya jata tha to tum maan-ne se inkaar kar dete thay aur jab uss ke sath dosaron ko milaya jata to tum maan letay thay ab faisla Allah buzurag o bartar ke haath hai """
40,13,"wohi hai jo tum ko apni nishanain dekhata hai aur aasman se tumahray liye rizaq nazil karta hai, magar ( inn nshanyon ke mushahiday se ) sabaq sirf wohi shakhs laita hai jo Allah ki taraf rujoo karne wala ho"
40,14,"( pas ae rujoo karne walo ) Allah hi ko poukaro apne deen ko uss ke liye khalis kar ke, khuwa tumhara yeh feal kafiroon ko kitna hi nagawaar ho"
40,15,"woh buland darjon wala, maalik arsh hai apne bundon mein se jis par chahta hai apne hukum se rooh nazil kar deta hai taakay woh mulaqaat ke din se khabardaar kar day"
40,16,"woh din jabkay sab log be parda hon ge, Allah se un ki koi baat bhi chhupi hui nah ho gi ( uss roz pukaar kar poocha jaye ga ) aaj badshahi kis ki hai? ( sara aalam pukaar utthay ga ) Allah wahid Qahar ki"
